member.name: T:Entia.Core.Documentation.ThreadSafeAttribute
member.summary:
Indicates that the target of the attribute is thread-safe.
-> In the case of a type, it indicates that all its public members (static and instance) are thread-safe.
-> In the case of a property or event, it indicates that all its public accessors are thread-safe.
Returns an enumerator that iterates through the collection.
